---
description: Palette lock and visual governance
globs:
  - "**/*.{tsx,ts,jsx,js,css,scss,md}"
alwaysApply: true
---
Always ask for or confirm the approved brand palette before defining principal UI colors. Use `config/project-palette.json` as the source of truth. Do not invent new principal brand colors outside the approved palette. Semantic exceptions for success, warning, error, and info are allowed.
